API

-----
Get All Orders

GET request to /api/orders

Sample Response:
[{
    id:1,
    name:'James',
    drink:'coffee'
},{
    id:2,
    name:'John',
    drink:'latte'
}]



-------
POST request to /api/orders
TYPE:JSON

Sample posts:
{
    name:'James',
    drink:'Coffee'
}


Sample Response:
{
    id:3,
    name:'Sammy',
    drink:'Latte'
}